            <div class="qa-wrapper">
              <h3 class="faq-question" tabindex="14" title="What exactly does DomaHub do?">
                What exactly does DomaHub do?</h3>
              <p class="faq-answer is-hidden">
                Put simply, DomaHub is a platform allowing domain name
                owners to rent out their domains to prospective renters.
                It's a communication and advertising platform for sellers,
                and a browse and shop marketplace for renters.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="qa-wrapper">
              <h3 class="faq-question" tabindex="15" title="How does DomaHub make money?">
                How does DomaHub make money?</h3>
              <p class="faq-answer is-hidden">
                DomaHub receives money every time a Basic listing is rented out
                as well as when a Premium listing is posted.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="faq-renting" class="faq-section">
            <h2 class="title is-normal has-borderBottom">Renting with DomaHub</h2>
            <div class="qa-wrapper">
              <h3 class="faq-question" tabindex="16" title="How can I rent a domain?">
                How can I rent a domain?</h3>
              <p class="faq-answer is-hidden">
                Go to our <a class="orange-link" href="/listings">listings page</a>
                to browse all current listings.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="qa-wrapper">
              <h3 class="faq-question" tabindex="17" title="How long can I keep the domain?">
                How long can I keep the domain?</h3>
              <p class="faq-answer is-hidden">
                You may only keep the domain for the amount of time you paid for.
                You will immediately lose ownership and control of the domain the
                second past your allotted time.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="qa-wrapper">
              <h3 class="faq-question" tabindex="18" title="What if I need it for longer than I originally planned?">
                What if I need it for longer than I originally planned?</h3>
              <p class="faq-answer is-hidden">
                All extensions must be negotiated and purchased prior to your current
                expiration date(s). However, if the domain has already been rented
                for the subsequent time slots, you may not steal those times away from
                others just because you currently have the domain rented.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="qa-wrapper">
              <h3 class="faq-question" tabindex="19" title="Can the domain owner sell the domain while I am renting it?">
                Can the domain owner sell the domain while I am renting it?</h3>
              <p class="faq-answer is-hidden">
                Domain rentals through DomaHub are legally binded by contract
                and may not - under any circumstances - be sold while a user
                has rented it.
              </p>
            </div>
