                Answer pending.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="faq-selling" class="faq-section">
            <h2 class="title is-normal has-borderBottom">Selling on DomaHub</h2>
            <div class="qa-wrapper">
              <h3 class="faq-question" tabindex="21" title="How do I start listing domains?">
                How do I start listing domains?</h3>
              <p class="faq-answer is-hidden">
                Once you have created an account and <a class="orange-link" href="/authorizestripe">
                verified Stripe</a> payments, you may create a listing by going to the
                <a class="orange-link" href="/listing/create">create listing</a> page.
                DomaHub offers two types of listings: Basic and Premium.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="qa-wrapper">
              <h3 class="faq-question" tabindex="22" title="What are the differences between basic and premium listings?">
                What are the differences between basic and premium listings?</h3>
              <p class="faq-answer is-hidden">
                A Basic listing is free to list, but has an 18% commission on sales.
                Basic listings have flat, fixed pricing which means DomaHub will decide
                its price. Additionally, Basic listings cannot be listed for hourly slots.
                A Premium listing costs &#36;5 a month to list, but DomaHub will not take any commission.
                Custom pricing as well as hourly pricing are both available to Premium listings.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="qa-wrapper">
              <h3 class="faq-question" tabindex="23" title="What happens if I find a buyer for my domain?">
                What happens if I find a buyer for my domain?</h3>
              <p class="faq-answer is-hidden">
                You may not sell your domain while it is being rented by a DomaHub
                user. However, if your domain is listed but not currently being rented,
                you may cancel the listing and sell it as you please.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="qa-wrapper">
              <h3 class="faq-question" tabindex="24" title="Can I cancel my listing while it's being rented?">
                Can I cancel my listing while it's being rented?</h3>
              <p class="faq-answer is-hidden">
                No you cannot immediately cancel any listing that is currently rented by a DomaHub user.
                However, you may cancel your listing for all dates following the current renters'
                schedule; effectively removing all future availability.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="qa-wrapper">
              <h3 class="faq-question" tabindex="24" title="How do I get paid?">
                How do I get paid?</h3>
              <p class="faq-answer is-hidden">
                As transactions occur, you will be paid automatically through your
                Stripe account. Go to your <a class="orange-link" href="/profile">profile</a>
                page to access more tools.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
